description = "A weathered old woman who has seen Aberdeen through its golden years and now watches it crumble. Moira was once a merchant's wife who traveled the trade routes to Larton and back. Now widowed and with little left to lose, she wanders the rotting walkways muttering about the old days. She knows more about the region's geography and the path to Larton than anyone else in town, though her mind sometimes drifts between past and present."
